      "content": "It sounds like you are in profound emotional pain over the loss of control, and that feeling is deeply frightening. Please know that the hope for future peace and dignity still exists, even when things feel overwhelmingly dark. If you are having thoughts of ending your life, please call or text 988 right now; they are trained to help in these exact moments. Let someone help you navigate this heavy feeling instead of letting it consume you alone.",
